parameters: \C[24][Cain]\C[0] Oh, she's come back to life.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] This is the village of Misa. Luna... I'm so glad you've come back to life.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] My body was supposed to have been torn apart by Zena... Why...
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] That's what we can't figure out.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] About ten days ago, a letter arrived. It was addressed to me.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Yes. The letter said, "Come to the village of Misa."

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] When we got here, there you were, Luna, lying in this bed. Everyone was so
surprised.

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Well... I thought about getting a handwriting analysis, but the letter burned
up.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] The day after the letter's seal was broken, it was magically turned to ash.
\C[24][Cain]\C[0] By the way, how's your body? Can you still use magic like before?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes, I'm fine. The wounds have healed without a trace, as if nothing ever
happened. It's unbelievable.

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] When I arrived here, there were a lot of fever reducers. It seems someone took
very good care of you.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Someone who could do such a thing... someone who cares about me so much...
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Oh yeah, while you were asleep, Luna, something big happened.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] The Knights of Messiah are going to lend their strength to the resistance of
Jupiterino.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Princess Alicia of Moduna officially signed it. The Knights of Messiah will be
dispatched to help the rebels in this country.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] That's great... Lady Ceres has... fulfilled our wishes.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Also... it seems that the resistance of Norvana was massacred by someone. Kyle-
san too...

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] But... according to an informant... it was discovered that the resistance of
Norvana was connected with Lucia and those from Valentia.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] So... they might have been assassinated by someone...
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Hey, Luna, there's more to the mysterious letter.

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] The letter also mentioned Mao and Mei. "I'm sorry I couldn't save them..." it
said.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Luna, are we going to visit Mao and Mei's graves?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes, I definitely want to go.
